808
00:37:40,800 --> 00:37:43,560
let's confine the two for a few days.

809
00:37:43,560 --> 00:37:45,840
You must not mistreat them.

810
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,360
- Yes.
- Hurry up and take them away.

811
00:37:47,910 --> 00:37:48,840
Let go of me.

812
00:37:49,950 --> 00:37:50,790
Mrs. Lu.

813
00:37:51,470 --> 00:37:52,310
Mrs. Lu.

814
00:37:53,670 --> 00:37:54,910
Let go of me.

815
00:37:58,320 --> 00:37:59,160
Mother,

816
00:37:59,710 --> 00:38:01,950
the two servants are punished.

817
00:38:01,950 --> 00:38:05,120
Shall we assign new servants to Nianbei?

818
00:38:06,520 --> 00:38:08,670
Find a couple of maids to take care of him.

819
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:10,040
Do we really need

820
00:38:10,040 --> 00:38:11,040
to take care of him personally?

821
00:38:11,040 --> 00:38:13,080
Meiting, that's inappropriate.

822
00:38:13,080 --> 00:38:14,000
No matter what,

823
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,800
Nianbei is a distinguished guest
of our family.

824
00:38:15,800 --> 00:38:16,710
If we neglect him,

825
00:38:16,710 --> 00:38:17,910
wouldn't that make us a laughingstock?

826
00:38:18,800 --> 00:38:19,800
Alright then,

827
00:38:19,800 --> 00:38:20,640
what do you suggest?

828
00:38:21,910 --> 00:38:23,600
Mother, how about this?

829
00:38:23,600 --> 00:38:25,520
The wharf has been closed recently anyway.

830
00:38:25,520 --> 00:38:26,840
So I'm free.

831
00:38:26,840 --> 00:38:29,280
I can take care of Nianbei.

832
00:38:30,080 --> 00:38:31,320
Yes, Mother.

833
00:38:31,320 --> 00:38:32,840
Nianbei is a man.

834
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:34,630
It's more convenient to have a man

835
00:38:34,630 --> 00:38:36,150
- take care of him.
- Indeed.

836
00:38:36,840 --> 00:38:38,600
If my brother-in-law gets too busy,

837
00:38:38,600 --> 00:38:40,000
I can lend a hand outside.

838
00:38:41,120 --> 00:38:42,520
Is that appropriate?

839
00:38:42,520 --> 00:38:43,870
Why wouldn't it be?

840
00:38:43,870 --> 00:38:46,190
Nianbei is a guest of you and Father.

841
00:38:46,190 --> 00:38:47,760
And now he's seriously ill.

842
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:49,760
We should be more attentive.

843
00:38:49,760 --> 00:38:51,630
Mother, Suying is right.

844
00:38:51,630 --> 00:38:53,600
We can't neglect Nianbei anymore.

845
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:55,320
Or else, when he wakes up,

846
00:38:55,320 --> 00:38:56,520
he might hold it against us.

847
00:38:56,520 --> 00:38:57,360
Yes.

848
00:38:57,670 --> 00:38:58,510
Alright.

849
00:38:58,910 --> 00:39:00,480
Then you two take care of him for a few days.

850
00:39:01,910 --> 00:39:02,750
Oh God.

851
00:39:03,280 --> 00:39:05,600
They cannot go unpunished.

852
00:39:05,600 --> 00:39:06,760
Now that they're punished,

853
00:39:06,760 --> 00:39:08,150
Nianbei is left...

854
00:39:08,150 --> 00:39:09,000
Mother,

855
00:39:09,000 --> 00:39:10,320
you have already done your utmost.

856
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:12,520
They can't find any fault with you.

857
00:39:12,520 --> 00:39:13,600
Yes.

858
00:39:13,600 --> 00:39:15,910
Today's matter must not be publicized.

859
00:39:15,910 --> 00:39:17,290
It would not sound good if it got out.

860
00:39:17,430 --> 00:39:19,120
It's hard to explain it to your father either.

861
00:39:19,950 --> 00:39:21,840
Confine them for a few days as a warning.

862
00:39:21,840 --> 00:39:23,040
Do not neglect them.

863
00:39:23,040 --> 00:39:23,910
Did you hear me?

864
00:39:23,910 --> 00:39:24,750
Yes.

865
00:39:27,280 --> 00:39:28,320
- Mother, slow down.
- Madam.

866
00:39:28,320 --> 00:39:29,190
Mother, slow down.

867
00:39:44,800 --> 00:39:46,520
Fortunately, we gave him
some medicine earlier.

868
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:48,390
Otherwise, he would have woken up by now.

869
00:39:49,390 --> 00:39:51,230
But if the medicine's effect doesn't last,

870
00:39:51,230 --> 00:39:52,360
he might wake up at any moment.

871
00:39:55,000 --> 00:39:57,320
Without my sister's commotion today,

872
00:39:57,910 --> 00:39:59,870
we probably wouldn't have
had this opportunity.

873
00:40:01,040 --> 00:40:02,600
Aren't you going to thank me?

874
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:03,800
I spent quite a bit of silver

875
00:40:03,800 --> 00:40:05,280
on that Blood Spirit Grass.

876
00:40:06,910 --> 00:40:07,750
Thank you?

877
00:40:16,120 --> 00:40:17,150
It's foolish of you

878
00:40:18,230 --> 00:40:21,040
to compete with me

879
00:40:22,040 --> 00:40:24,120
for the head of the family.

880
00:40:32,360 --> 00:40:33,200
Is...

881
00:40:33,560 --> 00:40:34,630
Is he about to wake up?

882
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:36,840
Quickly give him more medicine.

883
00:40:36,840 --> 00:40:38,280
It will be troublesome if he wakes up.

884
00:40:38,280 --> 00:40:39,870
Watch him here. I'll go get the medicine.

885
00:40:39,870 --> 00:40:40,710
Hurry up.

886
00:40:44,080 --> 00:40:45,870
Truly, you never know someone's true nature.

887
00:40:46,470 --> 00:40:47,800
We treat them sincerely,

888
00:40:47,800 --> 00:40:49,710
but they did such disgraceful things.

889
00:40:53,000 --> 00:40:53,840
Mother,

890
00:40:54,230 --> 00:40:56,120
what exactly are you worried about?

891
00:40:57,040 --> 00:40:59,190
Are you afraid that Nianbei will wake up

892
00:40:59,190 --> 00:41:00,520
and cause trouble for our family?

893
00:41:01,760 --> 00:41:03,430
What is his true identity

894
00:41:04,080 --> 00:41:05,710
that makes you and Father value him so much?

895
00:41:07,000 --> 00:41:08,520
Don't ask what you shouldn't ask.

896
00:41:09,190 --> 00:41:10,040
Even if I don't ask, I know.

897
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:12,840
Mother,

898
00:41:13,150 --> 00:41:14,230
tell me the truth.

899
00:41:15,230 --> 00:41:16,070
Is that Nianbei

900
00:41:16,800 --> 00:41:18,150
my father's illegitimate son?

901
00:41:18,150 --> 00:41:18,990
Meiting,

902
00:41:19,320 --> 00:41:20,160
don't speak nonsense.

903
00:41:21,040 --> 00:41:21,880
Alright,

904
00:41:22,670 --> 00:41:23,510
I won't say it anymore.

905
00:41:24,000 --> 00:41:24,950
But Mother,

906
00:41:24,950 --> 00:41:26,190
don't worry too much.

907
00:41:26,870 --> 00:41:28,800
They are just two servants.

908
00:41:28,800 --> 00:41:30,120
As you said,

909
00:41:30,120 --> 00:41:31,520
confine them for a few days as a lesson

910
00:41:32,760 --> 00:41:33,670
and then release them.

911
00:41:36,360 --> 00:41:37,200
How is it?

912
00:41:38,120 --> 00:41:40,040
Now he's completely weak

913
00:41:40,040 --> 00:41:41,430
without the slightest bit of strength.

914
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:43,600
That was close.

915
00:41:43,600 --> 00:41:45,520
Without this medicine,

916
00:41:45,520 --> 00:41:47,080
he might have woken up by now.

917
00:41:49,630 --> 00:41:50,520
What do you think

918
00:41:50,520 --> 00:41:51,630
we should do next?

919
00:41:52,230 --> 00:41:54,120
We can't just keep him sleeping forever.

920
00:41:54,120 --> 00:41:55,320
That's not very appropriate

921
00:41:56,470 --> 00:41:58,560
Do you plan to take care of him
for the rest of your life?

922
00:42:01,520 --> 00:42:02,360
What?

923
00:42:02,910 --> 00:42:04,390
Are you saying

924
00:42:04,390 --> 00:42:05,630
that we simply

925
00:42:06,230 --> 00:42:07,120
kill him?

926
00:42:08,470 --> 00:42:09,310
What do you think?

927
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:12,230
If you want to do it, go ahead.

928
00:42:12,870 --> 00:42:13,710
Don't drag me into it.

929
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:16,160
What do you mean?

930
00:42:17,470 --> 00:42:19,360
After all, he is my father's disciple.

931
00:42:20,840 --> 00:42:22,470
Although we don't know his identity,

932
00:42:23,080 --> 00:42:25,150
from his two followers,

933
00:42:25,150 --> 00:42:27,360
I can tell he's not an ordinary man.

934
00:42:27,360 --> 00:42:28,870
If you really kill them,

935
00:42:28,870 --> 00:42:30,430
whatever consequences arise,

936
00:42:30,430 --> 00:42:31,520
it's none of my business.

937
00:42:33,150 --> 00:42:34,430
You think you can wash your hands off it?

938
00:42:35,150 --> 00:42:36,470
Don't forget.

939
00:42:36,470 --> 00:42:38,390
Who came to me first to conspire this?

940
00:42:39,470 --> 00:42:41,190
We're just taking what we need
from each other.

941
00:42:44,600 --> 00:42:45,440
Yes.

942
00:42:46,120 --> 00:42:48,280
I know your ambitions, Suying.

943
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:49,800
And I believe you know my intentions.

944
00:42:50,390 --> 00:42:51,230
Don't worry.

945
00:42:52,600 --> 00:42:54,080
As long as we get rid of this thorn
in our side,

946
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:55,440
everything between us

947
00:42:56,430 --> 00:42:57,390
will be easy to resolve.

948
00:42:58,630 --> 00:43:00,910
Until we find out this person's identity,

949
00:43:01,520 --> 00:43:02,520
we can't harm him.

950
00:43:03,430 --> 00:43:04,870
So you mean

951
00:43:04,870 --> 00:43:06,000
to let him continue sleeping?

952
00:43:08,190 --> 00:43:09,150
Don't worry.

953
00:43:09,150 --> 00:43:10,840
As long as the effect of your medicine lasts,

954
00:43:11,360 --> 00:43:13,950
even if he doesn't die by then,

955
00:43:14,520 --> 00:43:15,710
he will become a cripple.

956
00:43:16,520 --> 00:43:19,230
What threat could he pose to us?

957
00:43:21,150 --> 00:43:21,990
Mr. Jiang.

958
00:43:26,670 --> 00:43:27,910
A big ship is approaching from afar.

